# Cursor — i18n & a11y

Authoritative source: [docs/ai/frontend/i18n-and-a11y.md](mdc:docs/ai/frontend/i18n-and-a11y.md).

## i18n

- The single source of truth is
  [`src/frontend/src/lib/i18n/en.json`](mdc:src/frontend/src/lib/i18n/en.json).
  All other locale files (`ar.json`, `de.json`, `es.json`, `fr.json`,
  `it.json`, `ja.json`, `ko-KR.json`, `pl.json`, `pt.json`, `ru.json`,
  `vi.json`, `zh-CN.json`, `cs.json`, `hi.json`) are **machine-translated**
  by the `auto-update-i18n` workflow. **Edit only `en.json`.**
- After editing `en.json`, regenerate the typed shape and key list:
  ```bash
  npm run i18n
  ```
  This regenerates `src/frontend/src/lib/types/i18n.d.ts` and the i18n key
  helpers. Commit both source and generated files together. Never edit the
  generated `.d.ts` by hand.
- Reference keys via property access only — never construct keys
  dynamically:

  ```svelte
  <button>{$i18n.core.text.save}</button>
  ```

  ```ts
  import { i18n } from '$lib/stores/i18n.store';
  import { get } from 'svelte/store';
  const msg = get(i18n).send.error.amount_too_low;
  ```

- Replacement placeholders use `$placeholder` syntax (see existing keys like
  `more_items: "+$items more"`). Substitute with `replacePlaceholders` from
  `$lib/utils/i18n.utils`.

## Forbidden

- Hard-coded English in any user-visible context: text node, `aria-label`,
  `title`, `alt`, `placeholder`, button copy, error messages.
- Concatenating sentences with `+` — use a single i18n key with placeholders.
- Editing any locale file other than `en.json` (the workflow overwrites them).
- Adding orphan keys — `frontend-remove-unused-components` and the i18n
  generator will eventually flag them.

## a11y baseline

- Real semantics: `<button>` for actions, `<a>` for navigation, `<label>`
  for inputs, headings in order. No bare clickable `<div>`.
- Every input has a label or `aria-label`.
- Icon-only buttons need `aria-label` (or visible text via `sr-only`).
- Decorative icons / images: `aria-hidden="true"` / `alt=""`.
- Don't kill focus outlines. Don't communicate state with color alone.
- Use the existing `$lib/components/ui/...` and `@dfinity/gix-components`
  primitives for dialogs / modals — they handle focus trap / escape / ARIA.
- `target="_blank"` ⇒ `rel="noopener noreferrer"`.
- Untrusted HTML ⇒ sanitize before `{@html …}`.
